Hi everyone, anybody knows how to get auto-translate for property value into Vast Email Cart Summary? For example I would like to translate line_item.name in each lang (en - es - it - fr ecc) . Will be so appreciate, this is the module: &lt;center&gt;&lt;h2 style="margin-top: 20px;text-color=#78C4BF" !important&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;div class="order-summary"&gt;
    {% email_each list="deal.line_items" item="line_item" %}
        &lt;table class="templateColumnWrapper" cellpadding="10" style="margin-top: 20px;"&gt;
            &lt;tbody&gt;
                &lt;tr&gt;
                    &lt;td class="column" style="vertical-align: middle;"&gt;
                        &lt;img src="{{line_item.hs_images}}" width="130" style="max-width: 130px;"&gt;
                    &lt;/td&gt;
                    &lt;td class="column summary" style="vertical-align: top;"&gt;
                        {{ module.order_summary }}
                    &lt;/td&gt;
                &lt;/tr&gt;
            &lt;/tbody&gt;
        &lt;/table&gt;
    {% endemail_each %}
&lt;/div&gt;
